    {
      "n": 10,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "10. Eij Akmizu-Kalna/ un\napfleppees Pihfhlos no ta KUN-\nGA Istruhzinaschanas / un no\ntahs Gohdibas wikka Augsti-\nbas.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 11,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "11. To Zilweko lepnas Azzis\ntaps paseuniotas/ un to Wihru\nAugstiba taps nolohzita/bet tas\nKUNGS buhs ween pa-augsti-\nnahts tanni Deena.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 12,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "12. Jo ta Deena ta Klunga\nZehaut buhs prett wiffu Lepnu\nun Augstu/ un prett wiffu kas\npa-augsfinajees/ ka tas tobh pa-\nsemmohts.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 13,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "13. Un prett wiffeem leeieem\nun augsteem Zeedra-Rohkeem ne\nLihbanus/ un prett wiffeem Oh-\nsoleem no Babsana.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 14,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "14. Un prett wiffeem aug-\nsteem Kalneem/ un prett wiffeem\nfszilteem Pakalneem.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 15,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "15. Un prett wiffeem aug-\nsteem Turxeem/ un prett wiffeem\nftipreem Muhreem.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 16,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "16. Un prett wiffahm Juhras\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 7,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "7. Laiwahn/ un prett wiffeem stat-\nsteem Tehleem.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 17,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "17. Un to Zilweku Lepniba\ntaps nolohzita / un to Wihru\nAugstiba taps paseunmota / be-\ntas KUNGS tween buhs tai\nDeena pa-augstinachts.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 18,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "18. Un tee Elka Deewi ees wif-\nfai bohja.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 19,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "19. Tad ees tee Akmiza-Kal-\nnu Allas/ un Semmes Plaisu-\nmos ta KUNGA Istruhzina\nfchanas deht/ un tahs Gohdiba-\nwixxa Augstibas deht/kad winsc-\nzelfees to Semmi istruhzinaht.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 20,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "20. Tai Deena nemettibs tai\nZilweks fawus Sudraba Elka-\nDeewus/ un fawus Selta Elka-\nDeewus/ ko tee few bij darrifichi\nKurnijo un Sitspahrno Prec-\nscha.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 21,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "21. Un ces Akmizu Schir-\nbas/ un Akmiza Kalnu Allas-\ntahs Istruhzinaschanas ta KUN-\nGA deht / un tahs Gohdiba-\nwixxa Augstibas deht / ka-\nwifsch zelfees to Semmi istrul-\nzinaht.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 22,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "22. Mittejeetees tad no i\nZilweka/ kam Dwalcba fawa-\nNahtis irr/ jo zik augsti tasje-\nle irr zeentjans.\n"
    }
